13. Information Architecture
BizDaily
│
├── Landing Page
│
├── Demo Access
│
└── Mobile Application
    │
    ├── Home Dashboard
    │
    ├── Record Today's Business
    │
    ├── Debt Management
    │
    ├── Business History
    │
