The MVP is intentionally small.

Every feature begins from the Home Dashboard.

14. Navigation Structure

The application follows a hub-and-spoke navigation model.

The Home Dashboard acts as the central hub.

From the Home screen, users access every feature through Quick Action cards.

Navigation flow:

Landing Page
      │
      ▼
Explore Demo
      │
      ▼
Home Dashboard
      │
      ├── Record Today's Business
      ├── Debt Management
      ├── Business History
      ├── Generate Reports
      └── Settings

There should be no desktop sidebar.

Navigation should feel like a native mobile application.

