20. Business Score

Display below the KPI cards.

Use a circular progress component.

Example:

91 / 100

Description

Business Score is calculated from:

Profit trends
Expense control
Sales consistency
Debt recovery
Daily reporting consistency

Only one score is displayed.

21. AI Insight Card

Display only ONE featured insight.

Examples

💡 Profit increased by 18% this week.

⚠ Expenses increased compared to last week.

📈 Sales reached the highest level this month.

💰 Outstanding debts reduced by ₦20,000.

Display one card only.

